Create the purchase receipt for the purchase order as follows:[anchor|#_5a48f678-622e-4c30-883c-135d7f9a0374] #While you are still viewing the purchase order on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PO_30_10_00|Purchase Orders] ([~/?ScreenId=PO301000|PO301000]) form, on the form toolbar, click '''Actions &gt; Enter PO Receipt'''. The system prepares the purchase receipt for the selected purchase order and opens it on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PO_30_20_00|Purchase Receipts] ([~/?ScreenId=PO302000|PO302000]) form. #Review the purchase receipt. #:Notice that the line with the ''URGDELIVERY'' service, which had been included in the purchase order, is absent in the purchase receipt. This is because the '''Require Receipt''' check box is cleared for the non-stock item on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\IN_20_20_00|Non-Stock Items] ([~/?ScreenId=IN202000|IN202000]) form. [anchor|#_72f0ea4d-e5b2-421b-a3b3-af5eb57aa310] #On the form toolbar, click '''Save'''. #Review the details of the prepared purchase receipt. Notice that the '''Create Bill''' check box is cleared in the Summary area. (You will create the bill manually in the next step.) #On the form toolbar, click '''Release'''. [anchor|#section_kzy_nsr_hlb] ==Step 3: Processing the AP Bill== Do the following to process the AP bill related to the purchase order:[anchor|#ol_gbz_nsr_hlb] #Return to the purchase order that you have processed earlier in this activity on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PO_30_10_00|Purchase Orders] ([~/?ScreenId=PO301000|PO301000]) form, and on the form toolbar, click '''Actions &gt; Enter AP Bill'''. The system generates an AP bill for the vendor of the goods and shows the created document on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\AP_30_10_00|Bills and Adjustments] ([~/?ScreenId=AP301000|AP301000]) form. #In the '''Description''' box, enter <tt>Purchase of jars with expedited delivery</tt>. #In the Summary area, clear the '''Hold''' check box. # On the form toolbar, click '''Release''' to release the bill. #Return to th